name: Slambook (For Sale)
description: “Slambook (For Sale)” is an 18-page e-zine (PDF). Triggered by the Facebook data breach reported in April 2021 which included my personal information and of at least 879,699 other Filipinos, I wanted to interrogate the many ways in which we make ourselves vulnerable in digital contexts. How separate are data and body? How much money is made in its trafficking?” Artist: Mac Andre Arboleda @asshulz | April 21, 2021
